        <owl:disjointWith rdf:resource="https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/National_implementations/DB/ETCS#ZbsReducedSpeedProperties"/>
        <rdfs:comment>Parameter for selecting a telegram by index during the planning process. E.g. big metal mass.</rdfs:comment>
