            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:comment>A raised construction for guiding cables across an obstacle.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment>bridgeNumber
The number of the cable bridge, if used.</rdfs:comment>
