        <owl:disjointWith rdf:resource="https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/ETCS#StandstillDetectionForShunting"/>
        <rdfs:comment>Encounter Prohibition System (EPS) is a signalling function that prevents trains encountering in a dual-track single-bore tunnel.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment>EpsReportingPoint
True when the signal reports to the system that prohibits train encounters in the tunnel. 
The signal may be located outside and in advance of the tunnel. 
de-DE: Meldepunkt f&amp;#252;r das Tunnelbegegnungsverbotssystem</rdfs:comment>
