        <owl:disjointWith rdf:resource="https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/ETCS#LeuPort"/>
        <owl:disjointWith rdf:resource="https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/ETCS#StandstillDetectionForShunting"/>
        <rdfs:comment>ETCS packet as defined in subset-026.
Used by either balise telegrams or RBC messages.
The end-user can use an existing XSD to instantiate XML of ETCS packets. See for instance the openETCS project (&lt;a href=&quot;$inet://https://github.com/openETCS/dataDictionary/blob/master/Artifacts/subset-026-7/Decoder/Delivery/SubsetFromWord/SubSet026_7.xml&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000ff&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;here)&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment>number
The number of the the ETCS packet according to subset 026-7.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>EtcsPacket</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    


