        <owl:disjointWith rdf:resource="https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/ETCS#StandstillDetectionForShunting"/>
        <rdfs:comment>Set of properties that apply to an ETCS signal.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment>acceptsRbcCommand
True if the light signal accepts a command from the interlocking to switch on the aspect dedicated to ETCS-guided trains.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment>isEtcsEntry
True if this signal is inside the ETCS L2 area and can be used for Level 2 Start of Mission.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>EtcsSignalProperties</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    


